com.thinkaurelius.titan.core.olap

Interface Combiner<M>


  • public interface Combiner<M>
    Combines two states into one combined state.

    Used to combine the gathered states in an OLAPQueryBuilder over the entire adjacency list of a central vertex into a single state.

    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
